+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S3-P02-T036 (CAC + National Data Administration A0 adapters; doc-type classifier; closes S3-P02; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Thirty-sixth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program and the LAST of S3-P02 (first A0 official adapters). Goal: add A0 adapters for the Cyberspace Administration (cac.gov.cn) and the National Data Administration (nda.gov.cn), covering front-line AI, cybersecurity, data-governance, and national-data-policy content, and distinguish a public consultation, a formal document, an interpretation, and news, keeping the official original text as primary. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; not wired to the worker, with the live cac classification from the dev environment. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: tools/adapter_cac_nda.py (a classify_doc_type distinguishing consultation, formal, interpretation, and news with an is_primary flag and consultation status and deadline; a CacNdaConnector on the T031 SDK with attachments; and build_registry for cac-gov and nda-gov), CAC_NDA_ADAPTER_SPEC.md, and evidence/ADP-S3-P02-T036/{fixtures/{consultation,formal,interpretation,news}.html, real_cac_smoke.json}. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S3-P02-T036/test-results/cac_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): the four document types are distinguishable, the official original text is primary since a consultation and a formal document are primary while an interpretation and news are not, and the consultation status is parsed as open with a deadline of 2026-08-10. An honest access note is recorded rather than faked: www.cac.gov.cn serves normally and the live classification of its real homepage links is correct (a leadership-inspection item as news and non-primary, and the AI-content-labelling consultation draft as a primary consultation), whereas www.nda.gov.cn returns a JS shell and rejects the default TLS (TLSV1_ALERT_PROTOCOL_VERSION), so nda-gov is registered but its health reports the live fetch blocked, needing a browser or an RSS/API entry -- its content is not fabricated. The live classification ran from the dev environment, so 0 cloud cost. This closes S3-P02. Cost (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
